data.description: Don't miss this great Southern Hills home! Are you looking for the perfect home to entertain family and friends? Well congratulations, your search is over! This beautiful home not only offers 3 large bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, it also has a bonus room and separate secluded dining room! While there, please be sure and enjoy the pleasant, covered patio with plenty room for entertaining and enjoy the inground swimming pool! You don't have to worry about swimmers dripping water on your new floors because they can use the separate pool bathroom just steps from the patio! This home is missing nothing but you!
